# Consumable Items

Adventures rarely go according to plan. The healing potion you drink when the cleric is down, the alchemist's fire you throw when surrounded, the antidote that saves you from poison—these single-use items often mean the difference between triumph and disaster.

Consumables provide immediate, powerful effects at the cost of being destroyed in use. Unlike permanent equipment that you carry throughout a campaign, consumables are tactical resources you spend when situations demand them.

